    <url>/2020/05/01/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0-1/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<img src="https://cdn.cultofmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/lisasimpsonapple.jpg" style="zoom:50%;" />



<h6 id="参考网址汇总"><a href="#参考网址汇总" class="headerlink" title="参考网址汇总"></a>参考网址汇总</h6><ul>
<li><p><a href="https://sspai.com/post/59337" target="_blank" rel="noopener">少数派在mac端搭建</a></p>
</li>
<li><p><a href="https://hexo.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo 官网</a></p>
</li>
<li><p><a href="https://docs.typo3.org/m/typo3/guide-contributionworkflow/master/en-us/Appendix/OSX/SSHKeyOSX.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">用的上的一些运行符</a></p>
</li>
<li><p><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/search?type=content&q=hexo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">知乎汇总</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
  <a id="more"></a>

<h6 id="Pay-attention"><a href="#Pay-attention" class="headerlink" title="Pay attention :"></a>Pay attention :</h6><ul>
<li>yarn 下安装 hexo 不需要启用 Root </li>
<li>github 仓库地址要完全与脚本温和</li>
<li>hexo init blog （ 默认初始化设置文件夹为 blog）</li>
<li>hexo 部署前，要把 SHH KEY 和脚本修改 </li>
<li>单篇推送出现问题，可删除重建 </li>
</ul>
<h6 id="其它工具"><a href="#其它工具" class="headerlink" title="其它工具"></a>其它工具</h6><ul>
<li>iterm - mac 终端</li>
<li>atom -改脚本</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n &#x3D;&#x3D; hexo new</span><br><span class="line">hexo g &#x3D;&#x3D; hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo s &#x3D;&#x3D; hexo server</span><br><span class="line">hexo d &#x3D;&#x3D; hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
